JOHANNESBURG – Racist Vicky Momberg will have to wait a week to learn her fate. She seemed to show no remorse for her offensive comments when appearing in the Randburg Magistrate's Court on Friday for sentencing procedures. READ: Vicki Momberg found guilty on four charges of crimen injuria In 2016, Momberg used the K-word repeatedly, as she verbally abused police officers, who had turned up to help her after a criminal incident. Momberg was charged after a video emerged of her insulting a police officer who was trying to help her after a smash and grab. In the video, she is heard complaining about the calibre of blacks. eNCA